WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.790
Hey, good morning family. How are y'all

00:00:02.800 --> 00:00:05.910
doing today? I have some things on

00:00:05.920 --> 00:00:07.590
my heart to talk to y'all about. I

00:00:07.600 --> 00:00:09.990
haven't done a video in a week. The

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:11.669
Lord told me, "I want you to seek me."I said,

00:00:14.960 --> 00:00:16.630
"Well, Lord, I have to make videos for the

00:00:16.630 --> 00:00:16.640
people."And

00:00:16.640 --> 00:00:18.390
he said, "Am I in charge of

00:00:18.400 --> 00:00:20.310
the channel or are you?"And I said,

00:00:20.320 --> 00:00:22.710
"Well, you are, of course."So he said,

00:00:22.720 --> 00:00:25.189
"I want you to pray and I want you to

00:00:25.199 --> 00:00:27.750
get filled back up."He said, "You

00:00:27.760 --> 00:00:30.390
cannot minister to the people out of

00:00:30.400 --> 00:00:33.110
your reserves. You have to make sure you

00:00:33.120 --> 00:00:35.510
pray and minister to the people in

00:00:35.520 --> 00:00:39.830
your overflow."It was

00:00:39.840 --> 00:00:41.910
just time for me to fill myself back

00:00:41.920 --> 00:00:43.590
up, getting in prayer and

00:00:43.600 --> 00:00:45.549
getting back to that secret place with

00:00:45.559 --> 00:00:48.670
him, not worrying about

00:00:48.680 --> 00:00:50.670
everything, seeking him for what's

00:00:50.680 --> 00:00:53.549
coming, and

00:00:53.559 --> 00:00:57.430
abiding in him and him abiding with

00:00:57.440 --> 00:00:59.510
me. It's been a beautiful

00:00:59.520 --> 00:01:04.509
time. I miss him

00:01:04.509 --> 00:01:04.519
because

00:01:04.519 --> 00:01:07.590
the distractions from so many

00:01:07.600 --> 00:01:09.830
things pulling on you all the time prevent you

00:01:09.830 --> 00:01:09.840
from taking

00:01:09.840 --> 00:01:12.950
that time and

00:01:12.950 --> 00:01:12.960
saying,

00:01:12.960 --> 00:01:15.670
"I refuse to allow things to keep

00:01:15.680 --> 00:01:18.390
pulling on me. I'm going to

00:01:18.400 --> 00:01:20.789
separate myself, not look at anything.

00:01:20.799 --> 00:01:23.030
I'm just going to focus on my

00:01:23.030 --> 00:01:23.040
relationship."It

00:01:23.040 --> 00:01:24.950
was interesting

00:01:24.960 --> 00:01:27.830
because even last night I called my

00:01:27.840 --> 00:01:29.270
wife out there while I was sitting

00:01:29.280 --> 00:01:31.109
outside on our back porch and I said,

00:01:31.119 --> 00:01:33.590
"Look at the trees because they are getting

00:01:33.600 --> 00:01:36.390
ready to start changing. You can see the

00:01:36.400 --> 00:01:40.230
signs and the

00:01:40.240 --> 00:01:43.109
beauty of

00:01:43.109 --> 00:01:43.119
life."Just

00:01:43.119 --> 00:01:45.590
taking the time to stop and look at

00:01:45.600 --> 00:01:48.389
the stars and look at what he

00:01:48.399 --> 00:01:51.510
created for us. It's a beautiful thing.

00:01:51.520 --> 00:01:55.389
In my prayer time, he visited me

00:01:55.399 --> 00:01:58.469
again. I don't

00:01:58.479 --> 00:02:01.149
know why I get these

00:02:01.159 --> 00:02:03.590
visitations; I make an

00:02:03.600 --> 00:02:06.230
atmosphere for him. I make a place for

00:02:06.240 --> 00:02:09.029
him to feel comfortable in my home by

00:02:09.039 --> 00:02:11.510
taking communion daily. We worship him

00:02:11.520 --> 00:02:13.510
all the time. My little

00:02:13.510 --> 00:02:13.520
girl—you've

00:02:13.520 --> 00:02:15.990
never

00:02:16.000 --> 00:02:18.390
met her, I don't let her

00:02:18.400 --> 00:02:20.790
come on here, she's a little

00:02:20.790 --> 00:02:20.800
one—but

00:02:20.800 --> 00:02:22.710
she walks around praising

00:02:22.720 --> 00:02:23.910
the Lord with me. She's the one

00:02:23.910 --> 00:02:23.920
who

00:02:23.920 --> 00:02:25.990
prayed for the dog to get raised

00:02:26.000 --> 00:02:28.070
from the dead outside

00:02:28.070 --> 00:02:28.080
when

00:02:28.080 --> 00:02:31.309
I stepped on it.

00:02:31.319 --> 00:02:33.630
In this

00:02:33.640 --> 00:02:36.710
time, I was seeking the Lord concerning

00:02:36.720 --> 00:02:39.910
the lost and praying for the salvations

00:02:39.920 --> 00:02:41.309
that I've seen

00:02:41.319 --> 00:02:44.430
coming. I'm going to make this

00:02:44.440 --> 00:02:46.550
video and not worry about the

00:02:46.560 --> 00:02:48.390
time. When I'm done, I'm done. If

00:02:48.400 --> 00:02:49.710
you don't want to watch it all, that's

00:02:49.720 --> 00:02:52.630
fine, but I have to tell you

00:02:52.640 --> 00:02:55.509
what the Lord has said. I'm going

00:02:55.519 --> 00:02:57.750
to go in the direction I feel

00:02:57.760 --> 00:02:59.509
the Holy Spirit lead me. I've

00:02:59.519 --> 00:03:02.390
always been time-conscious, but not

00:03:02.400 --> 00:03:05.149
this time.

00:03:05.159 --> 00:03:08.710
I was sitting outside

00:03:08.720 --> 00:03:10.390
praying and looking at

00:03:10.400 --> 00:03:12.470
the moon because there was a big, beautiful full

00:03:12.480 --> 00:03:15.270
moon here. I was looking

00:03:15.280 --> 00:03:19.270
at the beauty of everything and

00:03:19.280 --> 00:03:21.030
talking

00:03:21.040 --> 00:03:25.149
to him about the open door.

00:03:25.159 --> 00:03:28.070
I keep praying about the open door

00:03:28.080 --> 00:03:30.630
for the lost, taking off the blinders.

00:03:30.640 --> 00:03:33.190
The Lord's been revealing things to me;

00:03:33.200 --> 00:03:35.110
my wife's been reading me the books from

00:03:35.120 --> 00:03:37.710
Brother Hagin about how he prayed for the

00:03:37.720 --> 00:03:41.789
lost and how he prayed against the

00:03:41.799 --> 00:03:44.789
blinders, because the Bible says that

00:03:44.799 --> 00:03:47.509
the enemy blinds the eyes of the

00:03:47.519 --> 00:03:50.789
unsaved

00:03:53.280 --> 00:03:57.589
so they can't see. So I've been

00:03:57.599 --> 00:03:59.910
praying over the eyes of their

00:03:59.920 --> 00:04:01.350
understanding to be enlightened,

00:04:01.360 --> 00:04:03.350
just like in

00:04:03.350 --> 00:04:03.360
Ephesians,

00:04:03.360 --> 00:04:06.550
taking authority over the

00:04:06.560 --> 00:04:09.110
blinders where Satan has blinded

00:04:09.120 --> 00:04:12.229
people so they can see and

00:04:12.239 --> 00:04:13.910
have a revelation knowledge

00:04:13.920 --> 00:04:15.750
of Jesus Christ as their Lord and

00:04:15.760 --> 00:04:18.229
personal Savior. I was interceding

00:04:18.229 --> 00:04:18.239
for

00:04:19.509 --> 00:04:19.519
the

00:04:19.519 --> 00:04:21.670
lost—that's

00:04:21.680 --> 00:04:22.590
been my

00:04:22.590 --> 00:04:22.600
goal—and

00:04:22.600 --> 00:04:25.189
for the crash and the

00:04:25.199 --> 00:04:27.830
things I've seen coming, asking

00:04:27.840 --> 00:04:29.590
the Lord to lessen it so it wouldn't

00:04:29.600 --> 00:04:31.510
be so rough on people,

00:04:31.520 --> 00:04:33.749
standing in the

00:04:33.759 --> 00:04:35.950
gap like Abraham

00:04:35.960 --> 00:04:39.430
did for Sodom and Gomorrah.

00:04:39.440 --> 00:04:42.150
Ultimately it still came, but

00:04:42.160 --> 00:04:43.990
we have authority and power to

00:04:44.000 --> 00:04:46.230
stand in the gap. I was praying,

00:04:46.240 --> 00:04:49.430
interceding, "Father,

00:04:49.440 --> 00:04:51.909
I ask you to still shake and wake up

00:04:56.080 --> 00:04:58.469
the people so that we will have a

00:04:58.479 --> 00:05:01.510
great harvest of souls."Suddenly,

00:05:01.510 --> 00:05:01.520
as

00:05:01.520 --> 00:05:02.950
I was praying over the open

00:05:02.960 --> 00:05:07.350
door, the Lord

00:05:07.360 --> 00:05:10.150
showed me a vision of a normal door

00:05:10.160 --> 00:05:13.510
on a house. He said,

00:05:13.510 --> 00:05:13.520
"Brandon"—and

00:05:13.520 --> 00:05:15.350
it was like

00:05:15.350 --> 00:05:15.360
a

00:05:15.360 --> 00:05:18.150
light switch came

00:05:18.150 --> 00:05:18.160
on—he

00:05:18.160 --> 00:05:21.629
said, "Brandon, you're believing too

00:05:21.639 --> 00:05:24.870
small. I want an open door,

00:05:24.880 --> 00:05:28.230
but I want it to be a barn

00:05:28.230 --> 00:05:28.240
door."He

00:05:28.240 --> 00:05:32.510
showed me a massive barn with

00:05:32.520 --> 00:05:36.550
both doors open. Like

00:05:36.550 --> 00:05:36.560
when

00:05:36.560 --> 00:05:38.710
you open barn

00:05:38.710 --> 00:05:38.720
doors—huge,

00:05:38.720 --> 00:05:40.629
either they slide or

00:05:42.400 --> 00:05:45.590
swing open. He said, "I don't

00:05:45.600 --> 00:05:47.990
want a little 8ft door

00:05:47.990 --> 00:05:48.000
like

00:05:48.000 --> 00:05:49.670
you have in your house;

00:05:49.680 --> 00:05:52.390
I want a

00:05:52.400 --> 00:05:55.830
barn door."He showed me a massive,

00:05:55.840 --> 00:06:00.310
humongous harvest barn,

00:06:00.320 --> 00:06:02.390
like a massive dairy

00:06:02.400 --> 00:06:05.270
farm barn, and it had

00:06:05.280 --> 00:06:08.309
two huge open doors on it. All

00:06:08.319 --> 00:06:10.469
the way through, there were two more open

00:06:10.479 --> 00:06:12.790
doors.

00:06:12.800 --> 00:06:15.029
He said, "I'm going to

00:06:15.039 --> 00:06:16.189
show

00:06:16.199 --> 00:06:19.909
you what's inside the barn: the

00:06:19.919 --> 00:06:22.150
equipment that I'm equipping the

00:06:22.150 --> 00:06:22.160
end-time

00:06:22.160 --> 00:06:25.990
army

00:06:25.990 --> 00:06:26.000
for."I

00:06:26.000 --> 00:06:29.830
am the Lord of the harvest and I am

00:06:29.840 --> 00:06:33.189
going to harvest the souls, to harvest my

00:06:33.199 --> 00:06:35.430
people, the ones that are blinded.

00:06:40.160 --> 00:06:43.270
Inside the barn,

00:06:43.280 --> 00:06:47.189
his blood was

00:06:47.199 --> 00:06:49.670
applied

00:06:49.680 --> 00:06:53.670
over it like paint. Jesus Christ's blood made a

00:06:53.680 --> 00:06:56.230
way for you to be born again. He saved

00:06:56.240 --> 00:06:59.589
you by his blood; by his stripes, you're

00:06:59.599 --> 00:07:03.189
healed. He

00:07:03.199 --> 00:07:05.670
was crucified so you don't have to

00:07:05.680 --> 00:07:09.430
go to hell. He showed me the barn

00:07:09.440 --> 00:07:11.270
and it was the storehouse

00:07:11.270 --> 00:07:11.280
for

00:07:11.280 --> 00:07:12.950
everything. He

00:07:12.960 --> 00:07:14.950
was opening the barn doors, ready for

00:07:14.960 --> 00:07:17.830
the people to come in. Inside of

00:07:17.840 --> 00:07:21.029
that barn there were huge bales of

00:07:21.039 --> 00:07:24.550
massive golden hay

00:07:24.550 --> 00:07:24.560
representing

00:07:24.560 --> 00:07:26.790
the anointing

00:07:26.790 --> 00:07:26.800
and

00:07:26.800 --> 00:07:29.430
the outpouring of

00:07:29.440 --> 00:07:33.309
his spirit—a massive amount of

00:07:33.319 --> 00:07:36.270
the glory. There were glory hay

00:07:36.270 --> 00:07:36.280
bales

00:07:36.280 --> 00:07:39.990
inside of this barn. He

00:07:40.000 --> 00:07:41.430
told me, "I'm bringing forth

00:07:41.430 --> 00:07:41.440
those

00:07:41.440 --> 00:07:43.110
hay bales and it's going to

00:07:43.120 --> 00:07:44.790
bring forth the harvest.

00:07:44.800 --> 00:07:46.150
This is the

00:07:46.150 --> 00:07:46.160
equipment."The

00:07:46.160 --> 00:07:48.629
glory was going to

00:07:48.639 --> 00:07:51.189
be on the

00:07:51.199 --> 00:07:56.469
remnant, whoever's willing to be used.

00:07:56.479 --> 00:07:58.869
All of a sudden, Jesus appeared to

00:07:58.879 --> 00:08:03.029
me again, and this time he had

00:08:03.039 --> 00:08:05.670
overalls on.

00:08:07.919 --> 00:08:10.629
I said, "Lord, you have

00:08:10.639 --> 00:08:13.510
overalls on. I've never seen

00:08:13.520 --> 00:08:16.550
you wear overalls before."He had

00:08:16.560 --> 00:08:17.469
old

00:08:17.479 --> 00:08:21.430
blue jean overalls

00:08:21.440 --> 00:08:24.469
with a white shirt underneath

00:08:24.469 --> 00:08:24.479
and

00:08:24.479 --> 00:08:26.510
a red

00:08:26.520 --> 00:08:29.110
handkerchief in the back pocket.

00:08:29.120 --> 00:08:32.709
He had a

00:08:32.709 --> 00:08:32.719
straw

00:08:32.719 --> 00:08:35.589
cowboy hat on.

00:08:35.599 --> 00:08:37.990
Some of you might say, "I don't believe that,"but

00:08:37.990 --> 00:08:38.000
it's

00:08:38.000 --> 00:08:40.389
what I saw.

00:08:40.399 --> 00:08:43.670
Jesus came as a harvester, an

00:08:43.680 --> 00:08:46.470
old farmer.

00:08:46.480 --> 00:08:49.030
Before him was

00:08:49.040 --> 00:08:52.949
wheat,

00:08:52.949 --> 00:08:52.959
and

00:08:52.959 --> 00:08:55.590
it

00:08:55.600 --> 00:08:58.070
was huge,

00:08:58.080 --> 00:09:01.030
ripe, and bowing down

00:09:01.040 --> 00:09:03.829
because the grains of wheat were so

00:09:03.839 --> 00:09:06.550
heavy they were bending the

00:09:06.560 --> 00:09:09.910
stalks.

00:09:09.920 --> 00:09:14.070
It was beautiful, golden ripe wheat

00:09:14.080 --> 00:09:15.590
ready to be harvested.

00:09:18.880 --> 00:09:21.110
When he walked in the

00:09:21.120 --> 00:09:24.070
midst of it, the wheat started

00:09:24.080 --> 00:09:26.550
bowing down to him.

00:09:28.959 --> 00:09:31.910
It was swaying with him as he

00:09:31.920 --> 00:09:34.630
walked in the midst of it,

00:09:34.640 --> 00:09:37.269
moving with him.

00:09:37.279 --> 00:09:40.070
And all of a sudden he picked one of

00:09:40.080 --> 00:09:43.190
those pieces of wheat off of the

00:09:43.190 --> 00:09:43.200
stalk

00:09:43.200 --> 00:09:46.389
and he put it in his mouth, and it

00:09:46.399 --> 00:09:48.949
just dangled there, and he smiled real

00:09:48.959 --> 00:09:50.949
big at me. He said, "Brandon, the

00:09:50.959 --> 00:09:53.949
harvest is plentiful and the laborers are

00:09:53.959 --> 00:09:57.269
few. I am the Lord of the harvest, and my

00:09:57.279 --> 00:10:00.150
heart is the harvest, and there will be

00:10:00.160 --> 00:10:03.910
one last harvest before I

00:10:03.910 --> 00:10:03.920
come."And

00:10:03.920 --> 00:10:05.910
he showed me. He said, "I want you

00:10:05.920 --> 00:10:07.990
to see my hands."And ladies and

00:10:08.000 --> 00:10:10.829
gentlemen, I've never seen his hands

00:10:10.839 --> 00:10:14.310
before like this. He wanted

00:10:14.320 --> 00:10:15.870
me to focus on

00:10:15.870 --> 00:10:15.880
them.

00:10:15.880 --> 00:10:18.470
And he took his hands and he put

00:10:18.480 --> 00:10:21.670
them out before me. And on his hands,

00:10:21.680 --> 00:10:24.550
there were these massive holes where he

00:10:24.560 --> 00:10:27.030
had been crucified. There were big, big

00:10:27.040 --> 00:10:29.990
holes in his hands, and I could see

00:10:30.000 --> 00:10:32.949
through them. I could see

00:10:32.959 --> 00:10:35.190
the hole,

00:10:35.200 --> 00:10:37.910
and I could see through the hole and the

00:10:37.920 --> 00:10:41.030
wheat on the other side. You could see the

00:10:41.030 --> 00:10:41.040
wheat

00:10:41.040 --> 00:10:43.509
through the hole, it was so

00:10:43.519 --> 00:10:45.670
big. Now you think a little nail

00:10:45.680 --> 00:10:47.350
would be what they tacked him up

00:10:47.360 --> 00:10:50.870
there with; it was massive.

00:10:50.880 --> 00:10:54.069
It was like a humongous hole,

00:10:54.079 --> 00:10:57.110
but you could see through it

00:10:57.120 --> 00:10:59.030
all the way. And I

00:10:59.040 --> 00:11:01.190
could see glory going through. It looked

00:11:01.200 --> 00:11:03.269
like glory, like a light going through

00:11:03.279 --> 00:11:05.590
him because the light was

00:11:05.600 --> 00:11:07.829
shining inside of him like

00:11:07.839 --> 00:11:09.509
his blood or

00:11:09.519 --> 00:11:10.710
whatever. It was like

00:11:10.710 --> 00:11:10.720
a

00:11:10.720 --> 00:11:13.269
glory glow, and you could see it through

00:11:13.279 --> 00:11:15.910
the hole. And whenever he held his hands

00:11:15.920 --> 00:11:18.630
out like this, I could see the wheat

00:11:18.640 --> 00:11:21.350
moving through the hole. That's how big

00:11:21.360 --> 00:11:24.550
the hole was. And he said, "Brandon, I

00:11:24.560 --> 00:11:27.190
died for every single one of them. I

00:11:27.200 --> 00:11:29.269
died for all of them, and I desire

00:11:29.269 --> 00:11:29.279
that

00:11:29.279 --> 00:11:31.870
not one should perish, but all come to

00:11:31.870 --> 00:11:31.880
repentance."And

00:11:31.880 --> 00:11:34.069
he held his hands out

00:11:34.079 --> 00:11:36.630
and he said, "Will you help me bring in

00:11:36.640 --> 00:11:37.550
the

00:11:37.560 --> 00:11:42.350
harvest? Will you help me bring in the

00:11:42.350 --> 00:11:42.360
harvest?"And

00:11:42.360 --> 00:11:47.269
I said, "Lord,

00:11:47.279 --> 00:11:50.150
as for me and my house, we will do

00:11:50.160 --> 00:11:53.030
whatever it takes to help you bring in

00:11:53.040 --> 00:11:55.670
the

00:11:55.680 --> 00:11:58.630
lost."He

00:11:58.640 --> 00:12:01.430
says, "I know you will."He got

00:12:01.440 --> 00:12:04.230
excited. He said, "I know you

00:12:04.230 --> 00:12:04.240
will."And

00:12:04.240 --> 00:12:07.190
he was sitting there on the hill and he

00:12:07.200 --> 00:12:10.389
started singing me a song.

00:12:10.399 --> 00:12:12.470
He started singing a lullaby to the

00:12:12.480 --> 00:12:14.230
people, and it was really private to me.

00:12:14.240 --> 00:12:17.750
So I'll just say he

00:12:17.760 --> 00:12:19.750
kept saying, "I am the Lord of the

00:12:34.160 --> 00:12:42.680
harvest."He

00:12:50.760 --> 00:12:53.910
took his hands and he was

00:12:53.920 --> 00:12:56.310
telling me,

00:12:56.320 --> 00:12:58.870
"I died for

00:12:58.870 --> 00:12:58.880
them."Then

00:12:58.880 --> 00:13:01.750
he started

00:13:01.760 --> 00:13:03.750
singing me this song saying, "I am the

00:13:03.760 --> 00:13:05.910
Lord of the harvest."It was a

00:13:05.920 --> 00:13:07.629
beautiful

00:13:07.639 --> 00:13:10.310
song. And whenever he sang, I felt

00:13:10.320 --> 00:13:15.629
his

00:13:15.639 --> 00:13:22.509
presence so

00:13:22.519 --> 00:13:28.030
strong.

